*** Keywords ***
Highlight heading
    [Arguments]             ${locator}
    Update element style    ${locator}    border    2px solid red
    Highlight               ${locator}

Highlight Fancy
    [Arguments]             ${fancylocator}
    Update element style    ${fancylocator}    box-shadow    0 0 0 999999px rgba(0,0,0,.8)

Show Number
    [Arguments]    ${locator}      ${text}
    Add Dot
    ...            ${locator}
    ...            left=-8
    ...            text=${text}

Red Rect on
    [Arguments]             ${locator}
    Update Element Style
    ...                     ${locator}
    ...                     outline
    ...                     solid red 3px

Annotate
    [Arguments]        ${locator}        ${note}
    Add pointy note
    ...                ${locator}
    ...                text=${note}
    ...                position=right